# 11. Run Shell Commands

```yaml
---
- name: Run shell script
  hosts: all
  become: true

  tasks:

    - name: Copy script to remote host
      copy:
        src: /home/ubuntu/script.sh
        dest: /tmp/script.sh
        mode: '0755'

    - name: Execute script
      shell: /tmp/script.sh
      register: script_output  # result saved on this variable

    - name: Show script output
      debug:        # module to print variables and messages
        var: script_output.stdout_lines
```

