# 16. Kill Processes (Troubleshooting)

```yaml
---
- name: Kill process
  hosts: all
  become: true

  tasks:

    - name: Find process
      shell: "pgrep -f top"
      register: running_process

    - name: Show found PIDs
      debug:
        var: running_process.stdout_lines

    - name: Kill process
      command: kill {{ item }}
      loop: "{{ running_process.stdout_lines }}"
      ignore_errors: yes
```

