# 23. Handlers

```yaml
---
- name: Apache with handlers
  hosts: all
  become: true

  tasks:

    - name: Install Apache
      apt:
        name: apache2
        state: present
        update_cache: yes
      notify: Restart apache  # notify to execute a handler

    - name: Copy config file
      copy:
        src: /tmp/apache.conf
        dest: /etc/apache2/apache2.conf
      notify: Restart apache

  handlers:   # call the handler which is a special task. Executes the task if there was changes, not immediately. 

    - name: Restart apache
      service:
        name: apache2
        state: restarted
```

